{"tid":1046613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 華為控告美國政府無理封殺","createTime":"2019-03-04T11:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T02:38:50.000Z","uid":155095,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"752ba12f9c7e9b32015e70ea7362514f24ad6f19","tid":1046613,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T11:25:24.000Z","msg":"華為傳準備控告美國政府！<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》引述消息人士指，華為正準備在美國德州東區提出訴訟，控告美國政府禁止聯邦機構使用華為產品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2507552/org/9d9585ffe06b0944dff66501e57612fb.jpg/NmmhQb5o0KDpMZ4YxDoYz9PxSsm4FwfObys3JG8rNyQ?v=w1120r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2507552%2Forg%2F9d9585ffe06b0944dff66501e57612fb.jpg%2FNmmhQb5o0KDpMZ4YxDoYz9PxSsm4FwfObys3JG8rNyQ%3Fv%3Dw1120r16_9&h=6d54dce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為副董事長孟晚舟的代表律師，周日﹙3日﹚亦已經控告加拿大政府、加國邊境機構及聯邦警察，指稱孟晚舟遭到拘留、搜查及查問3小時，其憲法權利已受到侵害。<br />\n<br />\n華為拒絕對《紐約時報》的報道置評。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/302020/華為傳準備就被-封殺-向美國政府興訟\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A%2F302020%2F%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%82%B3%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%B0%B1%E8%A2%AB-%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA-%E5%90%91%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%88%88%E8%A8%9F&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4NjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=6f7a3bef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/302020/華為傳準備就被-封殺-向美國政府興訟</a>"},{"pid":"f87120446478332807f95162a003a1afc59b9d12","tid":1046613,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T11:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa20b2e0a6dbe7c650d843577d91d96fe61682e","tid":1046613,"uid":4917,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T11:31:49.000Z","msg":"唔用你都要解釋"},{"pid":"9f52bf420a84308d003330c75c4939dccdab8d0d","tid":1046613,"uid":70786,"like":77,"dislike":0,